latestIgtvVideos.title: Ear-ring and Dupatta combinations
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The best part about summers is wearing my colorful dupattas paired with ear-rings. Captured some of my favorites in this video ☺️ I love my dupattas and the testimony to that is - Even though my ethnic salwaar kameez becomes extremely old, I never throw the dupattas away and utilise them one way or the other. Also, all dupattas (except the golden one) are more than 5 years old ... like I always say, you must utilise what you have in your wardrobe and you'll be amazed at how many different combinations you can make.

All jewellery is either street shopped or bought from fests :) except the peacock ear-rings which I purchased from @myntra last year.

Let me know which combination you like the best, I could wear all of them over and over again.
.
.
Song : Buhe Bariyan by Jasmine Sandlas
